{"tid":2255291,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"鹽田看守所多番拒探望 4律師今向深圳市公安局投訴","createTime":"2020-10-23T12:05:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-23T16:25:43.000Z","uid":240362,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"b642c41774fe8d9cd9065b72b5f96b6d2d9f3dc8","tid":2255291,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T12:05:51.000Z","msg":"12名港人遭扣留在深圳鹽田看守所將滿兩個月，5名受家屬委託的律師昨爭取會面被拒，與之前一樣被告知當事人已另行委託律師。今早，盧思位、藺其磊、宋玉生等4名律師親赴深圳市公安局投訴鹽田看守所、鹽田區檢察院駐所檢察室，以及110接警中心違法。這已是一眾律師繼昨日下午向檢察機關控告看守所和鹽田公安分局後，今日到另一地點&ndash;&ndash;深圳市公安局作出投訴。<br />\n<br />\n5名受家屬委託的律師昨到鹽田看守所探訪當事人，但看守所以當事人已委託2名律師為由不獲安排探視，又拒絕透露當事人自行委託律師身份。5名律師期間因不滿看守所態度推諉，律師盧思位一度打內地報警電話110要求警監到場處理。同日下午，律師向檢察機關控告看守所和鹽田公安分局投訴看守所和警方的違法行為，檢察院指會盡快作出書面回覆。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20201023/KXOJQW4FUNHBNJK3YO37TDZSVA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20201023%2FKXOJQW4FUNHBNJK3YO37TDZSVA%2F&d=Z0jJ2Ci5UPqU8nDHOGo4vODT5CHOggjCyLUuLmpgHOg%3D&h=c009414c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20201023%2FKXOJQW4FUNHBNJK3YO37TDZSVA%2F&h=c13a44f1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20201023/KXOJQW4FUNHBNJK3YO37TDZSVA/</a>"},{"pid":"eed3176817c5318ba8e229335a0d88337edf78b2","tid":2255291,"uid":103965,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T12:06:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />勇者"},{"pid":"799ade75835211c04b2baaad70b96c757a1d1a38","tid":2255291,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T12:08:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c06ca